 for bestpractices and # Login Page Prompt for AI Development Tool

You are building a production-ready Login Page as part of a larger application (Gbox360) that includes Landing Page and Dashboard. Follow the requirements strictly to ensure robustness, accessibility, security, and runtime safety. All code generated must guard against null/undefined values before calling array methods, use proper defaults, and follow the runtime safety rules outlined in the project brief.

