- Card Design: white surface with light border, soft drop shadow, hover lift
- Navigation: not primary on Login Page; include links for Forgot password, Sign up, Request demo
- Interactive Elements: primary CTA in #0F172A; secondary actions with borders
- Accessibility: focus rings #93C5FD; high contrast text
- UX goals: fast access to sign-in, minimal friction, clear demo path

Connected Pages and Features:
- Landing Page and Dashboard integration
- User Authentication with session management, JWT, and OAuth placeholders

